<i>"OLD SONG" - Featuring artist: Ma Di</i>

508
00:43:49,570 --> 00:43:53,490
♫ <i>As I traverse this path without minding it</i> ♫

509
00:43:53,490 --> 00:43:56,970
♫ <i>My memory does all the hard work for me</i> ♫

